[thinking] **Considering class structure**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I’m thinking about the use of a static nested class inside a JUnit test class and how it relates to ClassUtils.isInnerClass. I wonder if it's capable of discovering the @ClassTemplate static nested class. To avoid depending on nested top levels, maybe a better approach would be to create a separate non-public top-level parameterized class within the same file. This seems worth exploring further!
